node.text:
We are having the ultimate Christmas Pamper Party! 💅
 
I’ve partnered with H&A and L.O.L. Surprise!, to launch the new L.O.L. Surprise! Beauty range now available from @Bootsuk💖
 
The new beauty range make for some thoughtful stocking fillers this Christmas, which includes the L.O.L. Surprise! Nail Varnish and L.O.L. Surprise! Body Art Set, perfect for you to host your own pamper party with your friends!
 
I’ve also been sent loads of other goodies like a L.O.L. Surprise! mug, hot chocolate, sweets and my absolute fav marshmallows!
 
Make sure you check out L.O.L. Surprise! range on @bootsuk – the perfect gifts for treating yourself or someone special this Christmas.
 
#ad #Boots #lolsurprise #ChristmasPamper Party #handa
